{"tid":1742437,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[中國結構工程專家] 滕錦光凌晨現身理大　對校園設施被破壞感難過","createTime":"2019-11-20T20:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T20:28:54.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"461e477bb5aa8428da9e9cc148d4ef1440dcf329","tid":1742437,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screen20Shot202019-11-1920at201.26.0220PM20copy_PIpr4_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreen20Shot202019-11-1920at201.26.0220PM20copy_PIpr4_1200x0.png&h=65f474bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會前主席曾鈺成、港大法律學院首席講師張達明、理工大學校董會主席林大輝以及一批中學校長，昨晚深夜陸續進入理工大學，籲校內人士和平離開。其後，遲遲未有現身的理大校長滕錦光於凌晨二時許終進入校園，呼籲留守者離開，又稱「覺得很難過，（校園）很多地方都被破壞」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>理大畢業禮 學生戴黑口罩上台 校長滕錦光拒握手</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/390929/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%A6%AE-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%88%B4%E9%BB%91%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%B8%8A%E5%8F%B0-%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E6%BB%95%E9%8C%A6%E5%85%89%E6%8B%92%E6%8F%A1%E6%89%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F390929%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%25A6%25AE-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2588%25B4%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%25BB%2595%25E9%258C%25A6%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%258B%2592%25E6%258F%25A1%25E6%2589%258B&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzrrngSbsgLaTM31cPJ1174U%3D&h=f08e91bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/390929/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%A6%AE-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%88%B4%E9%BB%91%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%B8%8A%E5%8F%B0-%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E6%BB%95%E9%8C%A6%E5%85%89%E6%8B%92%E6%8F%A1%E6%89%8B</a><br />\n<br />\n典禮進行期間，有一名女畢業生戴上黑色口罩上台，向林大輝鞠躬時亦有脫下口罩以表尊重，但她走到台上一則，打算與校長滕錦光握手合照時，滕當時退後一步，似有說話，惟未有與該名畢業生握手及合照。該名女學生隨後收起手，向滕鞠躬後步下台。<br />\n隨後，有另一名女畢業生配戴外科口罩上台，向林大輝鞠躬後，走向滕錦光的方向時，滕退後一步以手勢示意請對方下台。該名學生亦未有與滕合照及握手，向滕鞠躬後步下台階。"},{"pid":"b00b39245e352b077cd6c60abaf0951f6121bedd","tid":1742437,"uid":254450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:07:34.000Z","msg":"支藉校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e518e9667cea866ebccd29fc0c901c1564277c8f","tid":1742437,"uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b00b39245e352b077cd6c60abaf0951f6121bedd","tid":1742437,"uid":254450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:07:34.000Z","msg":"支藉校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:19:51.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣之前係南科大副校長<br />\n搞複制人果間野"},{"pid":"100d7017d4e3fb375dca125d757aac011111a48f","tid":1742437,"uid":206594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:21:31.000Z","msg":"啲老一輩對死物特別有同情心"},{"pid":"535498c5cb2b4dfd8a6790f06859052794dd153f","tid":1742437,"uid":108571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:21:56.000Z","msg":"點解啲藍絲特別對死物情有獨鍾<br />\n但對人命係冷漠？"},{"pid":"72c5f7fa5cfcc7ed5090fa8fa1ba71fa9c1a2980","tid":1742437,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T20:28:07.000Z","msg":"支那人就係咁on9<br />\n啲人俾人打到仆街當睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以呢場示威搞左5個月都仲未停<br />\n香港人同支那人既分別"},{"pid":"52c96e5e914fd097f776d3f66e1a738b124bedbc","tid":1742437,"u